    <title type="html"><![CDATA[北京女生笑点真低哦]]></title>
    <link href="http://namcheolix.github.com/blog/2010/10/28/post/"/>
    <updated>2010-10-28T20:49:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://namcheolix.github.com/blog/2010/10/28/post</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">一楼等电梯时碰见汤从实验室回来，聊了两句，旁边女生忍不住了一直在笑。</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">后来上了电梯，那女生还在笑，她旁边有个人认识她，问她为什么笑，她说刚才听了个笑话&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;于是给那人重复了我们的对话（我们还都在电梯上）</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">偶真有那么幽默么？</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">大家评定下。</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">================================================== ==</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">汤：你咋没来实验室</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">&#8230;&#8230;..</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">我：今天休息就不去了，明天再去。</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">汤：明天你要不去，我就去你床上骚扰你。</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">我:&#8230;&#8230;哎，今天要不你去伟伟床上睡吧。今天他不在，回家了。</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">汤：他回家干啥？</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">我：他回家结婚了。</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">汤：那么久没看见他，就结婚了？</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">我：是他回家看别人结婚。&#8230;&#8230;他跟人家送钱去了（此处此女生开始笑）</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">===============================================</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">汤下了电梯，一直说我有才&#8230;&#8230;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;"><span style="background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;font-size:100%;outline-width:0;outline-style:initial;outline-color:initial;vertical-align:baseline;display:inline;background-color:transparent;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:0 initial initial;margin:0;padding:0;">我无语</span></span></p>

<p> </p>
]]></content>
